	* procmap.c, procmem.c: Applied patch from Jeremy Lea.

	* prockernel.c, proctime.c: Applied patch from the FreeBSD 2.2.8
	ports collection.
	
	* procsignal.c: Applied patch from the NetBSD-current ports
	collection.

